Package: lava-server-doc
Architecture: all
Section: doc
Depends: ${sphinxdoc:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: documentation for lava-server
 This package contains an offline copy of the LAVA
 Manual available within LAVA server.
 .
 The manual includes use cases and examples to
 help users write tests for LAVA.
